# ADIN2111 Configuration
# Copyright (c) 2025 Murray Kopit <murr2k@gmail.com>

config ADIN2111
    bool
    default y if SSI
    depends on SSI
    help
      ADIN2111 Dual-Port 10BASE-T1L Ethernet Switch/PHY
      
      This enables emulation of the Analog Devices ADIN2111
      dual-port Ethernet switch with integrated PHYs.
      
      Features:
      - SPI slave interface
      - Dual 10BASE-T1L PHY ports
      - Internal L2 switch
      - Cut-through and store-and-forward modes
      - MAC filtering (16 entries)
      - IEEE 1588 timestamping support
      - Diagnostics and statistics